{"tid":911741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【後日開戰】留言「誓殺韓國瑜」 47歲工程師被拘","createTime":"2018-11-22T06:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T08:30:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b34ecdbc2eb4ceae14fd75388be04493ec96581c","tid":911741,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181122/large/1542864925_5dbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F1542864925_5dbf.jpg&h=1c6f8675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣九合一選舉在即，高雄市長選戰激烈，韓國瑜隨時成功入主高雄。有網友上周三（14日）在台大討論區「批踢踢」(PTT)一篇貼文下方留言，聲言要「高雄人誓殺韓國瑜報仇」。刑事局昨下午在台北市士林區逮捕47歲趙姓男子，他承認貼文，是針對選舉發表自己看法，只是寫了些情緒性字眼，強調沒想要做甚麼事。<br />\n<br />\n刑事局偵九大隊昨下午3時多在趙男住所將他約談到案，發現趙男是名正常上下班的工程師，即使韓國瑜陣營並未正式報案，但趙男言論已涉及恐嚇公眾罪遭送辦。<br />\n<br />\n另有民眾在fb發表「民進黨同志，我門暗殺韓國瑜&hellip;&hellip;」的文章，且類似內容已貼文多次，刑事局偵九大隊調查，發現IP資料來自新加坡，已請刑事局國際科駐外聯絡官與新加坡警方請求協助，查證發文者身份，目前已鎖定一名對象。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"f20f9985d088ce1c7eb43c32a1caae7a996d1071","tid":911741,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:36:41.000Z","msg":"反清復明 誓殺吳三桂"},{"pid":"400810595ca3e0a55eb8a1a2982b7df38d31a8c9","tid":911741,"uid":208722,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:37:58.000Z","msg":"清算型鍵國派末路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc36f1df31e6442a544013b55be16c39865fc555","tid":911741,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"連登仔D鍵國撚都冇咁武勇。<br />\n<br />\n太陽花，佔立法院，樣樣都贏晒班港豬。"},{"pid":"2f676109ce9824d225d190ea88628d69091d0d56","tid":911741,"uid":144075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"七生報國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5da53cc89345a3c2f04337801df6b45162a956","tid":911741,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"睇左韓國狗"},{"pid":"c3a1568f184597aef419edc09a5dab7859752c44","tid":911741,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"不誠實使用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21e8e3631ac588aa966a4df19c90e335581b947","tid":911741,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"幾時出埋槍擊"}]}